### Rota overview
GET http://localhost:3100/api/rota
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: rota-manager

### Rota overview (all active staff, filtered)
GET http://localhost:3100/api/rota?staffScope=all&role=STAFF&search=Casey
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: rota-manager

### Create six-week rota period
POST http://localhost:3100/api/rota/periods
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: rota-manager

{
  "startsOn": "2026-03-09",
  "label": "Spring rota block"
}

### Bank holiday sync status
GET http://localhost:3100/api/rota/bank-holidays/status
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: rota-manager

### Download rota template
GET http://localhost:3100/api/rota/template?startsOn=2026-03-09
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: rota-manager

### Export rota period
GET http://localhost:3100/api/rota/periods/{{rotaPeriodId}}/export
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: rota-manager

### Sync UK bank holidays
POST http://localhost:3100/api/rota/bank-holidays/sync
X-Staff-Role: ADMIN
X-Staff-Id: rota-admin

### Save rota assignment
POST http://localhost:3100/api/rota/assignments
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: rota-manager

{
  "rotaPeriodId": "{{rotaPeriodId}}",
  "staffId": "rota-alex-id",
  "date": "2026-03-10",
  "shiftType": "FULL_DAY"
}

### Bulk save rota assignments
POST http://localhost:3100/api/rota/assignments/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: rota-manager

{
  "rotaPeriodId": "{{rotaPeriodId}}",
  "staffId": "rota-alex-id",
  "changes": [
    {
      "date": "2026-03-09",
      "shiftType": "FULL_DAY"
    },
    {
      "date": "2026-03-10",
      "shiftType": "OFF"
    }
  ]
}

### Clear rota assignment
DELETE http://localhost:3100/api/rota/assignments/{{assignmentId}}
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: rota-manager

### Holiday requests list (mine)
GET http://localhost:3100/api/rota/holiday-requests?scope=mine
X-Staff-Role: STAFF
X-Staff-Id: rota-alex-id

### Holiday requests list (mine, approved only)
GET http://localhost:3100/api/rota/holiday-requests?scope=mine&status=APPROVED
X-Staff-Role: STAFF
X-Staff-Id: rota-alex-id

### Holiday requests list (all)
GET http://localhost:3100/api/rota/holiday-requests?scope=all
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: rota-manager

### Submit holiday request
POST http://localhost:3100/api/rota/holiday-requests
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: STAFF
X-Staff-Id: rota-alex-id

{
  "startDate": "2026-03-09",
  "endDate": "2026-03-15",
  "requestNotes": "Family trip"
}

### Approve holiday request
POST http://localhost:3100/api/rota/holiday-requests/{{holidayRequestId}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: rota-manager

{
  "decisionNotes": "Approved and covered on the workshop bench."
}

### Reject holiday request
POST http://localhost:3100/api/rota/holiday-requests/{{holidayRequestId}}/reject
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: ADMIN
X-Staff-Id: rota-admin

{
  "decisionNotes": "Too many people away that weekend."
}

### Cancel holiday request
POST http://localhost:3100/api/rota/holiday-requests/{{holidayRequestId}}/cancel
X-Staff-Role: STAFF
X-Staff-Id: rota-alex-id

### Rota import preview
POST http://localhost:3100/api/rota/import/preview
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: rota-manager

{
  "fileName": "rota-export.csv",
  "spreadsheetText": "Week commencing,09/03/2026,,,,,\nName,Mon 09/03,Tue 10/03,Wed 11/03,Thu 12/03,Fri 13/03,Sat 14/03\nClosed day,,,,,Closed: Special bank holiday,\nAlex Turner,Full,AM,Holiday,Off,Off,PM\nJordan Patel,Off,Full,Off,PM,Off,Off"
}

### Rota import confirm
POST http://localhost:3100/api/rota/import/confirm
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: rota-manager

{
  "fileName": "rota-export.csv",
  "previewKey": "replace-with-preview-key",
  "spreadsheetText": "Week commencing,09/03/2026,,,,,\nName,Mon 09/03,Tue 10/03,Wed 11/03,Thu 12/03,Fri 13/03,Sat 14/03\nClosed day,,,,,Closed: Special bank holiday,\nAlex Turner,Full,AM,Holiday,Off,Off,PM\nJordan Patel,Off,Full,Off,PM,Off,Off"
}
